ISLAMABAD, May 29 (APP): Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif Sunday said democracy was strengthened with the local government elections in Balochistan.
In a tweet on social media platform Twitter, he said, “With LG elections in Balochistan, democracy stands strengthened.”“People’s active participation in polls shows their trust in state institutions to provide security & ensure smooth conduct of polls. I admire law enforcement agencies for their role. Pakistan Zindabad,” he added.
